---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'healthcare-system', text: 'Healthcare System', level: 2 },
  { id: 'visa-requirements', text: 'Visa Options', level: 2 },
  { id: 'insurance-requirements', text: 'Insurance Requirements', level: 2 },
  { id: 'recommended-providers', text: 'Recommended Providers', level: 2 },
  { id: 'costs', text: 'Expected Costs', level: 2 },
  { id: 'scenarios', text: 'Real-World Scenarios', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'Common Questions', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Myanmar Insurance Guide', href: '/countries/myanmar/insurance' },
  { title: 'Insurance for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors' },
  { title: 'Thailand for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/thailand' },
  { title: 'Vietnam for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/vietnam' },
  { title: 'Laos for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/laos' },
];

const providerColumns = [
  { key: 'provider', header: 'Provider' },
  { key: 'entryAge', header: 'Max Entry Age' },
  { key: 'renewal', header: 'Renewal' },
  { key: 'monthlyFrom', header: 'From (65-69)' },
  { key: 'myanmarFit', header: 'Myanmar Fit' },
];

const providerRows = [
  { provider: 'Cigna Global', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'MMK$1.05M-1.5M/mo', myanmarFit: 'Essential' },
  { provider: 'BUPA Global', entryAge: '79', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'MMK$1.23M-1.75M/mo', myanmarFit: 'Essential' },
  { provider: 'Allianz Care', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'MMK$945K-1.35M/mo', myanmarFit: 'Essential' },
  { provider: 'Now Health', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: 'MMK$878K-1.25M/mo', myanmarFit: 'Essential' },
];

const costColumns = [
  { key: 'category', header: 'Expense' },
  { key: 'monthly', header: 'Monthly' },
  { key: 'annual', header: 'Annual' },
];

const costRows = [
  { category: 'International Insurance (65-69)', monthly: 'MMK$945K-1.5M', annual: 'MMK$11.3M-18M' },
  { category: 'International Insurance (70-74)', monthly: 'MMK$1.3M-2M', annual: 'MMK$15.6M-24M' },
  { category: 'International Insurance (75-79)', monthly: 'MMK$1.74M-2.68M', annual: 'MMK$20.9M-32.2M' },
  { category: 'Medical Evacuation', monthly: 'N/A', annual: 'MMK$100M-300M' },
  { category: 'Thailand Hospital', monthly: 'Per trip', annual: 'Common destination' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Health Insurance for Seniors in Myanmar 2026 | Retirement Guide"
  description="Guide to health insurance for seniors in Myanmar. Ancient temples, limited healthcare, current instability, and coverage for visitors 65+."
  headline="Health Insurance for Seniors in Myanmar"
  subheadline="Myanmar offers ancient Bagan temples, Buddhist culture, and stunning landscapes—but current political instability and extremely limited healthcare make it unsuitable for senior retirement. Visit with extreme caution."
  heroImage="/images/countries/myanmar-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Compare Senior Plans →"
  ctaButtonHref="/go/cigna-global"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Current Situation Warning</h2>
  <p>
    Myanmar is currently experiencing significant political instability following the 2021 military coup. Civil conflict, restricted travel, and deteriorating healthcare infrastructure make it unsuitable for senior retirement. This guide is for historical context and potential future reference only.
  </p>

  <p>
    Before 2021, Yangon had some healthcare options. Bagan and Mandalay offered cultural experiences. Currently, most Western embassies advise against travel. Healthcare has significantly deteriorated. Thailand evacuation is essential for any visitors.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-900 mb-3">Critical Warning</h3>
    <ul class="text-red-800 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Political situation:</strong> Ongoing instability since 2021 coup</li>
      <li><strong>Healthcare:</strong> Severely deteriorated; many facilities closed</li>
      <li><strong>Travel advisories:</strong> Most countries advise against travel</li>
      <li><strong>Banking:</strong> International transactions very difficult</li>
      <li><strong>Recommendation:</strong> NOT suitable for senior retirement currently</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2 id="healthcare-system">Myanmar Healthcare System</h2>
  <p>
    Myanmar healthcare was already limited before 2021—now severely compromised. International hospitals have closed or reduced services. Public system collapsed in many areas. Any serious condition requires immediate evacuation to Thailand (Bangkok). Do not rely on local healthcare.
  </p>

  <p>
    Thailand is essential backup—Bangkok is 1.5-hour flight from Yangon with world-class hospitals. International insurance with comprehensive Thailand coverage and evacuation is absolutely non-negotiable.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-2">Healthcare Collapse</h3>
    <p class="text-amber-800 mb-0">
      Myanmar's healthcare system has largely collapsed since 2021. Many doctors fled or stopped working. International facilities closed. Bangkok evacuation essential for ANY medical need. Do not visit without comprehensive evacuation coverage.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="visa-requirements">Visa Options</h2>
  <p>
    Visa options (when travel is possible):
  </p>

  <h3>Tourist Visa</h3>
  <p>
    28-day e-visa when available. Currently restricted. Check current status before planning.
  </p>

  <h3>Business Visa</h3>
  <p>
    For business purposes. Very limited currently.
  </p>

  <h3>Retirement Options</h3>
  <p>
    No formal retirement visa ever existed. Long-term stays were difficult even before 2021.
  </p>

  <h2 id="insurance-requirements">Insurance Requirements</h2>
  <p>
    If travel is undertaken:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Essential:</strong> Comprehensive international coverage</li>
    <li><strong>Evacuation:</strong> Thailand evacuation coverage critical</li>
    <li><strong>War/civil unrest:</strong> Check policy exclusions carefully</li>
    <li><strong>Cancellation:</strong> Trip cancellation coverage important</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Insurance Strategy for Myanmar</h3>
    <p class="text-blue-800 mb-0">
      If traveling to Myanmar (against most advice), comprehensive international insurance with Thailand evacuation is absolutely essential. Check policy exclusions for civil unrest. Ensure 24/7 assistance line. Consider whether any insurance is adequate for current conditions.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="recommended-providers">Recommended Insurance Providers</h2>
  <p>
    For any travel to Myanmar, comprehensive coverage essential:
  </p>

  <ComparisonTable columns={providerColumns} rows={providerRows} />

  <h3>Important Considerations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Check exclusions:</strong> Civil unrest may not be covered</li>
    <li><strong>Verify coverage:</strong> Confirm Myanmar is covered by policy</li>
    <li><strong>Thailand network:</strong> Ensure strong Bangkok access</li>
    <li><strong>Consider alternatives:</strong> Thailand offers similar temples, better safety</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Consider Thailand Instead</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Thailand offers excellent Buddhist temples, healthcare, and retirement options.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/insurance-for/seniors/in/thailand" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Thailand Senior Guide</a>
      <a href="/go/cigna-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-neutral-700 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Insurance Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="costs">Expected Insurance Costs</h2>
  <p>
    Insurance costs if traveling (MMK ~2,100 to USD officially, black market rates vary):
  </p>

  <ComparisonTable columns={costColumns} rows={costRows} />

  <h2 id="scenarios">Hypothetical Scenarios</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Pre-2021 Scenario (Historical)</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> Long-term visitor before coup. Yangon.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> Cigna Global with Thailand evacuation.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Status:</strong> Most such visitors have left.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Current Recommendation</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> Senior interested in Myanmar.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Recommendation:</strong> Visit Thailand instead—similar temples, excellent healthcare.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Alternative:</strong> Wait for situation to stabilize.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="faqs">Common Questions</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Can I retire to Myanmar?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        No—Myanmar never had formal retirement visa, and current instability makes long-term residence impossible for Westerners. Healthcare has collapsed. Most expats have left. Not a viable retirement destination.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Is any travel possible?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Limited—some tourists visit but against most government advice. Flight access limited. Internal travel restricted. Situation unpredictable. Most embassies recommend deferring travel. Check current conditions before any plans.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">What are the alternatives?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Thailand—excellent Buddhist temples (Chiang Mai, Sukhothai), world-class healthcare, easy retirement visa. Cambodia—Angkor Wat temples, growing healthcare. Laos—Buddhist culture, affordable, Thailand evacuation nearby.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Will Myanmar improve?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Unknown—situation remains volatile. International pressure ongoing. Resolution timeline unclear. Monitor news. Beautiful country with rich culture—hopefully will become accessible again. Currently not recommended.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Explore Safe Alternatives</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Consider these countries with similar culture and better conditions.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/insurance-for/seniors/in/thailand" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Thailand Guide</a>
      <a href="/insurance-for/seniors/in/cambodia" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-neutral-700 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Cambodia Guide</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-0">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Myanmar is currently experiencing significant political instability. Most governments advise against travel. This guide is for informational purposes only. Always check current travel advisories before any travel planning.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
